---
import Page from "../../layouts/Page.astro";
---

<Page title="Data Policy | Botify Life" description="Read our data policy for Botify Life.">
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-blue-700">Data Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-6 text-gray-700">
      This Data Policy explains how Botify Life ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, stores, and protects your data when you use our website and services.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-blue-600">What Data We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-1">
      <li>Personal information you provide (such as name, email, and contact details)</li>
      <li>Usage data (such as pages visited, features used, and interactions)</li>
      <li>Technical data (such as browser type, device information, and IP address)</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-blue-600">How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-1">
      <li>To provide and improve our services</li>
      <li>To personalize your experience</li>
      <li>To communicate with you about updates, offers, and support</li>
      <li>To analyze usage and improve website performance</li>
      <li>To ensure security and prevent misuse</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-blue-600">How We Protect Your Data</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      We use industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, or loss. Access to your data is limited to authorized personnel only.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-blue-600">Data Sharing</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      We do not sell your personal data. We may share data with trusted partners and service providers only as necessary to operate our services, comply with legal obligations, or protect our rights.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-blue-600">Your Rights</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-1">
      <li>You can request access to, correction, or deletion of your personal data</li>
      <li>You can opt out of marketing communications at any time</li>
      <li>You can contact us for any questions or concerns about your data</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-blue-600">Updates to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      We may update this Data Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-8 text-gray-600">
      If you have any questions about our data practices, please contact us at <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 underline">Contact Us</a>.
    </p>
  </main>
</Page>